---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Privacy Policy | Active Oahu Tours';
const pageDescription = 'Active Oahu Tours privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you book kayak tours, e-bike adventures, or equipment rentals in Kailua, Oahu.';
---

<BaseLayout
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  image="/images/og-privacy.jpg"
>
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-ocean/10 text-ocean text-sm font-bold uppercase rounded-full mb-4">
        Legal
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-navy mb-6">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-navy/60 mb-4">
        Last updated: May 30, 2026
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-navy/70">
        <p>
          Active Oahu Tours ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. 
          This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website 
          <strong>activeoahutours.com</strong> or book our kayak tours, e-bike adventures, and equipment rentals.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-navy">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        
        <h3>Personal Information You Provide</h3>
        <p>When you book a tour or rental, contact us, or sign up for our newsletter, we may collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Name and contact details</strong> (email address, phone number)</li>
          <li><strong>Booking information</strong> (tour date, number of guests, special requirements)</li>
          <li><strong>Payment information</strong> (processed securely through FareHarbor — we never store full credit card numbers)</li>
          <li><strong>Communications</strong> you send to us (emails, messages, reviews)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Information Collected Automatically</h3>
        <p>When you visit our website, we may automatically collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Usage data</strong> (pages visited, time on site, referring URLs)</li>
          <li><strong>Device information</strong> (browser type, operating system, screen resolution)</li>
          <li><strong>IP address</strong> and general location data (city/region level only)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We use <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong> for privacy-first analytics — no cookies, no tracking across sites, no personal data collection.</p>

        <h2 class="text-navy">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Process and manage your tour and rental bookings</li>
          <li>Send booking confirmations, reminders, and important updates about your reservation</li>
          <li>Respond to your questions, comments, and customer service requests</li>
          <li>Send marketing communications (only if you've opted in — you can unsubscribe anytime)</li>
          <li>Improve our website, services, and customer experience</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations and enforce our policies</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-navy">3. How We Share Your Information</h2>
        <p>We do <strong>not sell, rent, or trade</strong> your personal information. We may share your information with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>FareHarbor</strong> — our booking platform provider, who processes reservations and payments on our behalf</li>
          <li><strong>Service providers</strong> — companies that help us operate our business (email delivery, website hosting)</li>
          <li><strong>Legal authorities</strong> — when required by law or to protect our rights and safety</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-navy">4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information, including:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>SSL/TLS encryption</strong> for all data transmitted through our website</li>
          <li><strong>Secure payment processing</strong> through FareHarbor (PCI-DSS compliant)</li>
          <li><strong>Access controls</strong> limiting staff access to personal data on a need-to-know basis</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-navy">5. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
        <p>
          Our website uses <strong>minimal cookies</strong> — only those required for core functionality:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>FareHarbor booking widget</strong> — necessary cookies for the booking process</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — security and performance cookies (no tracking)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do <strong>not</strong> use third-party advertising cookies, retargeting pixels, or cross-site tracking. 
          We use Cloudflare Web Analytics, which is <strong>cookie-free</strong> and doesn't track individual users.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-navy">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Access</strong> the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li><strong>Correct</strong> inaccurate or incomplete information</li>
          <li><strong>Delete</strong> your personal data (subject to legal retention requirements)</li>
          <li><strong>Opt-out</strong> of marketing communications at any time</li>
          <li><strong>Data portability</strong> — receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:aloha@activeoahutours.com" class="text-ocean hover:underline">aloha@activeoahutours.com</a>.</p>

        <h2 class="text-navy">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our tours welcome families with children, but our website and booking system are not directed at children under 13. 
          We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 without parental consent. 
          Parents or guardians booking on behalf of minors are responsible for providing consent.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-navy">8. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          Our website may contain links to third-party websites (FareHarbor, TripAdvisor, social media). 
          We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these sites. Please review their privacy policies separately.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-navy">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. 
          We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-navy">10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, contact us at:</p>
        <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 border border-sand not-prose">
          <p class="font-semibold text-navy">Active Oahu Tours</p>
          <p class="text-navy/70">130 Kailua Road, Kailua, HI 96734</p>
          <p class="text-navy/70">
            <a href="tel:+18085551234" class="text-ocean hover:underline">(808) 555-1234</a>
          </p>
          <p class="text-navy/70">
            <a href="mailto:aloha@activeoahutours.com" class="text-ocean hover:underline">aloha@activeoahutours.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-ocean hover:bg-ocean-light text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-xl transition-all shadow-lg"
        >
          Back to Home
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
